name: Teeks for Geeks
tag_list: it, it-training, geek, geeks, cloud, tech, techie, coding, network
overview: Teeks for Geeks is the ultimate social learning haven for geeks around the world. Whether you are interested in coding, networking or comprehensive IT expertise, Teeks for Geeks provides a social environment where you can find self-paced, personalized, interactive IT training courses for only a few bucks. Teeks for Geeks offers specialized bite-sized training units (teeks) that let you interact with elite gurus who teach you about how to harness the power of the latest technological advancements. You can also meet like-minded classmates in a cloud-powered social environment where technically diverse crowds of IT geeks assemble to collaborate, teach and expand their skill sets.
